public class AutomaticTagFormElementTag
extends BaseTag

Automatic form element tag. Chooses the tag to draw the control based on the information supplied in the component.

Author:
Jevgeni Kabanov (ekabanov at araneaframework dot org)
Jsp.tag:
name = "automaticFormElement" body-content = "JSP" description = "Automatic form element which dynamically draws correct form element tag."
